des:
Crypto Prices is an Alexa skill used to retrieve cryptocurrency prices for most popular cryptocurrencies prices on demand. Currently you can ask for live prices for any of the following 15 crypto assets, Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP, Dogecoin, Binance Coin, Cardano, Polkadot, Binance USD, Uniswap, Litecoin, Chainlink, Ethereum Classic, Tron, Monero, and Cosmos Atom.
